<!--
    AML MODULE DEMO DATA — transaction_screening
    =====================================================================
    Loaded automatically when the module is installed in demo mode.
    To force-reload on an existing install run:
        Settings → Technical → Scheduled Actions
        → "Reload Demo Data" (if available), or reinstall in demo mode.

    What this file creates
    ──────────────────────
    1. Three demo customer partners (retail, individual, corporate)
    2. Two AML configuration records (one active, one archived)
    3. Nine demo transactions spread across the three customers
    4. Three customer behavioral profiles (one per customer)
    5. Three velocity alerts   in states: open / reviewed / escalated
    6. Three structuring alerts in states: open / false_positive / escalated
    7. Four anomaly alerts       in states: open / reviewed / escalated / closed
-->
<odoo>
    <data>

